              <Properties>
                <Configuration>
                  <Text>Task 1: You may want to keep the cards suit and value as individual fields for easier manipulation.  Also useful will be to keep not just the face value of card 10, J, Q, K, A along with their respective hierarchical values 10, 11, 12, 13, 14)</Text>
